<db:abstract>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-core-coresettings.xml">CoreSettings</db:link> class holds settings related to core data handling process.</db:para>
<db:para>This type was introduced in Qt 6.0.</db:para>
</db:abstract>
